Hi all,
I'm preparing the report of the track results. My raw notes are at https://docs.google.com/document/d/12-O_5dOcGY8QQric4FTCQZbeNbcilsY8DAGC8ji7MeI/edit?usp=sharing. Please feel free to change the bullets to readable text, add your own observations, change what you know better, edit any clear mistakes, and propose any other changes.
Great notes! Adding a couple of points I jotted down, but lots of good stuff already there.
Everyone please add your names to the list of participants. This will help us communicate that we had great attendance!
Thank you everyone for your contributions to the report. I copied it over to the Connectathons master report.
